            "category": "Category 9: Advice and precaution",
            "start_offset": 9599,
            "end_offset": 9655,
            "annotation_id": "PK_131"
        },
        {
            "decision": "4. You have been given medications for pain control. ",
            "category": "Category 5: Drug related",
            "start_offset": 9658,
            "end_offset": 9709,
            "annotation_id": "PK_132"
        },
        {
            "decision": "Please do not drive, operate heavy machinery, or drink alcohol while taking these medication",
            "category": "Category 9: Advice and precaution",
            "start_offset": 9711,
            "end_offset": 9804,
            "annotation_id": "PK_133"
        },
        {
            "decision": "As your pain decreases, take fewer tablets and increase the time between doses",
            "category": "Category 9: Advice and precaution",
            "start_offset": 9806,
            "end_offset": 9884,
            "annotation_id": "PK_134"
        },
        {
            "decision": ". This medication can cause constipation, so you should drink plenty of water daily and take a stool softener (such as colace) as needed to prevent this side effect.  ",
            "category": "Category 9: Advice and precaution",
            "start_offset": 9886,
            "end_offset": 10048,
            "annotation_id": "PK_135"
        },
        {
            "decision": "Call your surgeons office 3 days before you are out of medication so that it can be refilled",
            "category": "Category 9: Advice and precaution",
            "start_offset": 10051,
            "end_offset": 10143,
            "annotation_id": "PK_136"
        },
        {
            "decision": "These medications cannot be called into your pharmacy and must be picked up in the clinic or mailed to your house.  ",
            "category": "Category 9: Advice and precaution",
            "start_offset": 10146,
            "end_offset": 10259,
            "annotation_id": "PK_137"
        },
        {
            "decision": "Please allow an extra 2 days if you would like your medication mailed to your home.",
            "category": "Category 9: Advice and precaution",
            "start_offset": 10262,
            "end_offset": 10344,
            "annotation_id": "PK_138"
        },
        {
            "decision": "5. You may not drive a car until cleared to do so by your surgeon",
            "category": "Category 9: Advice and precaution",
            "start_offset": 10347,
            "end_offset": 10412,
            "annotation_id": "PK_139"
        },
        {
            "decision": "6. Please keep your wounds clean",
